		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Oziphantom wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">In that if I take a US NES game I can't use it on a Famicom</div><br />But but but... actually you can. Though this is not officially supported, you can do this by using only <em>official products</em>, that if you ply open certain carts of <em>1st party</em> NES games, you get a game cart that's directly playable on a Famicom and an <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gyromite#Famicom_Adaptor" class="postlink">adapter</a> to play Famicom games on a NES.

		

